<p>We use your personal data for the following purposes:</p>

<ul>
    <li>To provide and maintain our calendar</li>
    <li>To send you notifications about your calendar</li>
    <li>To fix bugs and improve our calendar</li>
    <li>To communicate with you about your calendar</li>
    <li>To conduct research and analysis to improve our calendar</li>
    <li>To comply with applicable laws and regulations</li>
</ul>

<p>How we share your personal data</p>

<p>We do not share your personal data with third parties without your consent, except in the following cases:</p>

<ul>
    <li>We may share your personal data with our service providers who help us provide and maintain our calendar</li>
    <li>We may share your personal data if required by law or regulation</li>
    <li>We may share your personal data if necessary to protect our rights or property or the rights or property of others</li>
</ul>
